{"tid":567860,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦遊戲時會突變斷電重新開機（已排除某的原因）","createTime":"2018-02-21T08:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T16:23:19.000Z","uid":79569,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5930a94db22ba815d24a3d48a4a07a054ac782fa","tid":567860,"uid":79569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:40:39.000Z","msg":"CONFIG如下：<br />\n7700k 4.8Ghz and 4.5Ghz - 1.255v<br />\nMSI Z270 GAMING M7<br />\nTeam Ram 8GB 2400 *1<br />\nZOTAC 970 4GB<br />\nSeasonic X Series 650W (2015年1月買入)<br />\n<br />\n係遊戲時間時會突然斷電重新開機（遊戲開始30分鐘左右，CS：GO同GTA 5都係咁既情況），BIOS會RESET，遊戲時CPU&amp;GPU溫度正常無異常!<br />\n<br />\n開始時以為係OC唔穩定，之後試下跑LinX，次數為50次係無問題！<br />\n<br />\n之後DEFAULT BIOS SETTING下無OC，遊戲情況下都係一樣會重啟！<br />\n<br />\n又試過將GPU既CORE -100MHz RAM -50MHz都係會重啟!<br />\n<br />\n再之後我用WINDOWS 內置TEST RAM既工具SCAN一次RAM，結果都係無事<br />\n<br />\n再再之後去CHECK WINDOWS LOG，每當有呢個情況下個EVENT LOG都有一個叫Windows Kernel event ID 41 error The system has rebooted without cleanly shutting down first既記錄<br />\n<br />\n請問大家咁既情況係咪火牛既問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae72bb722a4c52225f341991679a4d39151e796","tid":567860,"uid":31017,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"我ge經驗應該係cup風扇積塵太高<br />\n引致cup過熱重啟<br />\n用core temp測試下係咪cpu過熱先"},{"pid":"d9ffe13fd7394735f449d7f42bad1821fc50f2bf","tid":567860,"uid":79569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bae72bb722a4c52225f341991679a4d39151e796","tid":567860,"uid":31017,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"我ge經驗應該係cup風扇積塵太高<br />\n引致cup過熱重啟<br />\n用core temp測試下係咪cpu過熱先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"溫度正常啊....我LINX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas